name: OBJ1
text: To demonstrate that 3 mg LY900018 is non-inferior to 1 mg IMG for the proportion of patients achieving treatment success from insulin-induced hypoglycemia using a non-inferiority margin of 10%

name: OBJ2
text: To compare the safety and tolerability of 3 mg LY900018 with 1 mg IMG

name: OBJ3
text:
To characterize the PK profile of 3 mg LY900018
compared to 1 mg IMG

name: OBJ4
text:

compared to 1 mg IMG

name: OBJ5
text: Explore the formation of anti-glucagon antibodies to glucagon

name: OBJ6
text: To evaluate the recovery from clinical symptoms of hypoglycemia
